         <abstract id="aspace_889d8c309c078273f1f468d553606c33">The papers consist of materials relating to George Peabody Wetmore and his family. Correspondence and other papers document the lives of several of Wetmore's ancestors and reflect his interest in New England history. The papers also include letter books and account books of the mercantile firms of Prosper Wetmore &amp; Brothers and Joseph and Joshua Grafton.</abstract>
